Package com.hhstechgroup.tests.regressionBaseline.ii_IndividualEnrollment

This Package contains test classes covering all the test stories for Individual Enrollments.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IndividualEnrollmentApproveTest
    This class contains a test that uses a data provider to get a submitted Individual Enrollment and Approves it.
    IndividualEnrollmentDenyTest
    This class contains a test that uses a data provider to get a submitted Individual Enrollment and Denies it.
    IndividualProviderAppealApproveProcessTest
    This class contains a test that uses a data provider to get a Denied Individual provider, Creates an appeal request for that provider and approves it.
    IndividualProviderAppealDenialProcessTest
    This class contains a test that uses a data provider to get a Denied Individual provider, Creates an appeal request for that provider and Denies it.
    IndividualProviderCocProcessForTest
    This class contains a tests which uses the data provider to get a Approved Individual provider, Creates a CoC for retro active adjustment and Approved it, Creates a CoC for Identifying Information and Denies it and Also verifies the COC Ownership and Program Participation tab messages
    IndividualProviderCreateAndApproveSiteVisitTest
    This class contains a test that uses a data provider to get a Approved Individual provider, Creates an Site Visit for that provider and approves it.
    IndividualProviderCreateCoCAndAppealApprovalTest
    This class contains a test that uses a data provider to get a Coc denied for an Individual Provider, Creates an appeal request for that provider and approves it.
    IndividualProviderInternalUserOperationTest
    This class contains a multiple test that uses the data provider to get a submitted Individual provider, Performs screens for that Individual provider and Changes Status of application to Request for Additional Information, Provider Re-submit the enrollment and Internal User Denies it
    IndividualProviderPaymentFeeVerificationTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to submit an Individual enrollments and Verifies the Instate and Out state Payment Fees for the same.
    IndividualProviderPreConditionSetupForIndividual
    This test class sets the Systems Option configuration for Individual Provider.
    IndividualProviderReenrollmentProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an Approved Individual provider and Terminates it, ReEnrolls the Terminated provider and Approves it.
    IndividualProviderRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider for submitting an Individual Enrollment.
    IndividualProviderRetroActiveAdjustmentApprovalTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a submitted Individual enrollment and approve the enrollment retroactively.
    IndividualProviderRetroActiveRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to register a new Provider and, creates and submits an Individual enrollment retroactively.
    IndividualProviderRevalidationProcessTest  
    IndividualProviderTerminateSuspendReactiveProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an Active Individual Provider,verifies the changing of a Individual Provider status from 'Suspend to Reactive' and 'Terminate to Reactive'.
